    "To understand the work activities associated with ChatGPT usage, we mapped messages to one of the 332 O*NET Intermediate Work Activities (IWA), with an additional option of Ambiguous to account for situations where the user message lacked sufficient context.",
    "22 We then used the official O*NET taxonomy to map these classified IWAs to one of the Generalized Work Activities (GWA).",
    "We do not show the shares for the following GWAs as there were fewer than 100 users sending messages for each category and group them into Suppressed.",
    "Figure 14 presents the share of messages that belong to each GWA, in descending order.",
    "Nearly half of all messages (45.2%) fall under just three GWAs related to information use and manipula-"
